  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Follow up via ultrasonic abdoman after patients who were giagnosed and treated as
      periappendicular abcess and refused to be operated later on in the &quot;interval period &quot;. To ass
      what occured to their appendics ?
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      During the last 10 years patients were hospitalized and treated with antibiotics due to the
      diagnosis of periappendicular abcess. they were invited to be operate after wards
      -appendectomy, electively few weeks later on. All these patients refused to be operated. What
      happend to their appendics few months or years later on via ultrasonic abdomen view??
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
